WEBVTT

00:06.581 --> 00:09.281
(Capital City)

00:09.551 --> 00:10.400
Zhao Si,

00:10.401 --> 00:11.571
this is the Dou's Residence.

00:11.921 --> 00:13.110
I'm the clan leader

00:13.111 --> 00:14.651
and Shiying's older brother.

00:15.431 --> 00:17.781
If you wish to attend the wedding,
do come.

00:17.801 --> 00:20.581
(Dou Shishu, Dou Family's Fifth Master)
Otherwise, do as you please.

00:20.981 --> 00:24.121
(Zhao Si, Zhao Family's Eldest Son)
Do as I please?

00:26.801 --> 00:27.941
My silly sister,

00:28.441 --> 00:29.891
do you understand that now?

00:30.521 --> 00:33.461
When your husband was studying
in Chanxi,

00:33.761 --> 00:36.971
your best friend took
very good care of him.

00:37.041 --> 00:39.611
Now she's marrying into the Dou Family.

00:40.081 --> 00:42.171
What kind of wedding is this?

00:42.951 --> 00:43.820
Guqiu,

00:43.821 --> 00:45.440
(Wang Yingxue)
you know

00:45.441 --> 00:47.870
how I've struggled all these years
in Chanxi

00:47.871 --> 00:49.251
and being treated with contempt.

00:49.441 --> 00:52.101
Recently, my father was promoted.

00:52.271 --> 00:54.101
I could've easily married into
a noble family.

00:54.671 --> 00:57.580
But I value Shiying's kindness.

00:57.581 --> 00:58.761
(Dou Shiying,
Dou Family's Seventh Master)

00:58.901 --> 01:01.581
I'm willing to marry into the Dou Family
as a concubine

01:01.881 --> 01:03.931
because of the deep bond
we shared as best friends.

01:04.331 --> 01:07.941
It's normal for a man
to have multiple wives.

01:08.751 --> 01:10.211
Rather than someone else,

01:10.471 --> 01:13.301
why not let it be you and me
who understand each other?

01:15.521 --> 01:16.661
Understand each other?

01:19.721 --> 01:22.301
Is this how you repay my understanding?

01:28.521 --> 01:30.571
You know she is my close friend.

01:32.271 --> 01:34.411
You know he is my husband.

01:37.641 --> 01:38.750
How could you…

01:38.751 --> 01:40.101
Why not?

01:40.361 --> 01:42.030
Scholars of Shiying's age

01:42.031 --> 01:43.411
already have many children.

01:43.721 --> 01:45.331
You've been married for almost ten years

01:45.641 --> 01:47.360
and you only have a daughter.

01:47.361 --> 01:48.620
If he doesn't take a concubine,

01:48.641 --> 01:50.491
do you want to break

01:50.721 --> 01:51.910
the Dou's bloodline?

01:51.911 --> 01:53.051
Shishu,

01:53.531 --> 01:54.470
stop it.

01:54.471 --> 01:56.021
According to our law,

01:56.031 --> 01:58.370
a concubine can only be taken
with the main wife's consent.

01:58.371 --> 02:00.021
My sister has the right to not allow it.

02:00.191 --> 02:02.301
Miss Wang's father, Wang Xingyi,

02:02.601 --> 02:05.661
is the current Grand Secretary,
Wu Yifen's student.

02:06.081 --> 02:08.461
He has just been promoted
to a fourth-rank official.

02:08.471 --> 02:09.781
Marrying into the Wang family

02:10.641 --> 02:13.171
would be a great help
to Shiying's career.

02:13.271 --> 02:14.480
How could you not allow it?

02:14.481 --> 02:17.221
So it turns out you think
the Zhao Family is insignificant

02:18.391 --> 02:19.360
to be of any help.

02:19.361 --> 02:20.501
Guqiu,

02:21.151 --> 02:22.480
I never meant that.

02:22.481 --> 02:24.150
A husband leads and his wife follows.

02:24.151 --> 02:25.270
This is the natural order of things.

02:25.271 --> 02:26.411
The Dou Family needs

02:26.481 --> 02:27.891
this marriage.

02:28.391 --> 02:29.571
Nonsense!

02:29.671 --> 02:31.891
Over the years, how much money

02:31.961 --> 02:33.920
did the Zhao Family contribute

02:33.921 --> 02:35.870
to Dou Shiying's studies and career?

02:35.871 --> 02:39.080
How much of that is shady?

02:39.081 --> 02:41.061
Is that part of natural order too?

02:41.321 --> 02:43.430
If you dare pressure my sister again,

02:43.431 --> 02:47.291
I will submit a formal petition.

02:48.151 --> 02:48.990
Zhao Si,

02:48.991 --> 02:50.261
stop being reckless!

02:50.871 --> 02:52.291
Are you willing

02:52.981 --> 02:54.541
to destroy everything for your sister?

02:54.761 --> 02:56.011
You can try me.

02:57.241 --> 02:58.851
Times have changed.

02:59.551 --> 03:00.691
If it comes to that,

03:01.961 --> 03:04.291
let's see who has no way out.

03:12.081 --> 03:13.221
I didn't lie to you, right?

03:13.521 --> 03:14.691
Ms. Longevity, don't worry.

03:14.871 --> 03:16.171
You can rely on my father.

03:17.481 --> 03:19.381
This concerns the Dou clan's future.

03:19.431 --> 03:21.411
Fifth Uncle won't give up easily.

03:21.921 --> 03:23.661
We need to solve this quickly.

03:23.991 --> 03:26.821
Or it'll be too late
when Wang Xingyi arrives.

03:28.391 --> 03:30.381
I only wanted a place to belong.

03:30.551 --> 03:32.691
I never expect to hurt my best friend

03:33.081 --> 03:34.621
or put Shiying in a difficult spot.

03:35.361 --> 03:36.320
Guqiu,

03:36.321 --> 03:38.291
if you really can't forgive me,

03:39.031 --> 03:41.291
then grant me a strip of white silk
so I can end my life.

03:44.321 --> 03:46.381
Stop pretending.

03:47.201 --> 03:48.411
If you really want to die,

03:51.711 --> 03:52.851
take it.

03:53.641 --> 03:54.770
Guqiu,

03:54.771 --> 03:56.741
when did you become so cold-hearted?

04:03.481 --> 04:04.621
Yingxue!

04:04.921 --> 04:06.061
Throw it away.

04:06.081 --> 04:08.261
- Yingxue.
- Let me die!

04:08.271 --> 04:09.741
My love,

04:10.431 --> 04:12.581
let me die!

04:14.341 --> 04:15.481
Father.

04:19.081 --> 04:20.221
Ms. Longevity?

04:26.521 --> 04:28.091
I missed you.

04:29.881 --> 04:31.981
Who is this lady on the floor?

04:32.321 --> 04:33.941
Tell her

04:35.441 --> 04:36.861
who is that woman to you.

04:38.591 --> 04:39.731
She...

04:43.321 --> 04:45.451
She is a guest here
to offer her congratulations.

04:46.591 --> 04:47.731
Shiying...

04:48.001 --> 04:50.470
Then why are both of you unhappy

04:50.471 --> 04:52.131
because of this guest?

04:54.561 --> 04:55.701
- We're not.
- We're not.

05:00.031 --> 05:02.501
Father, Mother.

05:04.441 --> 05:05.581
Ms. Tuo,

05:05.881 --> 05:07.941
please escort this lady out first.

05:08.031 --> 05:10.111
I wish to speak
with Father and Mother for a while.

05:10.881 --> 05:12.021
Ah, that's right.

05:12.081 --> 05:14.200
Since she is a guest,
let's send her off for now.

05:14.201 --> 05:16.091
- After they're done talking,
- Please get up.

05:16.321 --> 05:17.910
- we will inform her.
- I'm not leaving.

05:17.911 --> 05:19.030
Come on, get up.

05:19.031 --> 05:21.061
Let me go! I'm not leaving!

05:23.761 --> 05:24.901
- She...
- Yingxue!

05:29.121 --> 05:30.261
Yingxue.

05:30.911 --> 05:31.910
I can't catch my breath.

05:31.911 --> 05:34.301
Yingxue, it's all right. I'm right here.

05:35.121 --> 05:36.421
You're having an asthma attack.

05:38.761 --> 05:41.621
Yingxue developed asthma
after closely tending to me

05:41.631 --> 05:44.061
when I had a cold.

05:44.831 --> 05:45.971
Guqiu,

05:46.961 --> 05:48.261
I can't just ignore her.

07:19.621 --> 07:22.020
=Blossom=

07:22.021 --> 07:23.900
(Adapted from the novel
"Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

07:23.901 --> 07:27.161
=Episode 2=

07:28.701 --> 07:29.830
(Perpetual Bloom)
Seventh Madam,

07:29.831 --> 07:32.120
it's the main wife's duty to hold
the ceremony of taking a concubine.

07:32.121 --> 07:33.760
Fifth Master had me send these over.

07:33.761 --> 07:35.781
So please prepare accordingly.

07:36.621 --> 07:38.440
My aunt hasn't agreed
to take a concubine yet.

07:38.441 --> 07:39.761
Why should she prepare for it?

07:40.001 --> 07:41.741
Get out! Leave.

07:42.561 --> 07:43.701
Mother.

07:43.881 --> 07:45.331
If you refuse to accept,

07:45.681 --> 07:47.501
with Miss Wang's family background,

07:47.681 --> 07:50.451
they would never allow her
to be an unacknowledged mistress.

07:50.681 --> 07:51.941
Even if she were willing,

07:52.201 --> 07:53.590
her father, Wang Xingyi,

07:53.591 --> 07:55.131
would never agree.

07:55.351 --> 07:58.181
If things drag on,
this matter will left unsolved.

08:01.151 --> 08:02.291
Ms. Longevity,

08:02.831 --> 08:04.861
why are you so mature for your age?

08:06.521 --> 08:07.520
My father says

08:07.521 --> 08:08.861
Uncle is a bad man.

08:09.231 --> 08:10.680
You should divorce him

08:10.681 --> 08:12.281
and save yourself from all this torment.

08:14.031 --> 08:16.520
Divorce is always seen

08:16.521 --> 08:18.571
as a trivial matter to a man.

08:19.881 --> 08:21.531
But for Ms. Longevity and me,

08:22.271 --> 08:24.861
it would mean a lifetime
of gossip and disgrace.

08:26.231 --> 08:28.211
I can't ruin Ms. Longevity's future.

08:30.231 --> 08:32.821
Besides, after a divorce,

08:33.161 --> 08:35.101
children always belong to the husband.

08:36.111 --> 08:37.381
How could I bear that?

08:38.281 --> 08:40.131
I'm not afraid of anything else

08:40.351 --> 08:41.931
but of you feeling tormented.

08:42.231 --> 08:43.701
If you want to divorce,

08:43.751 --> 08:45.381
I will go with you.

08:45.401 --> 08:46.931
Uncle is well-versed in the law.

08:47.081 --> 08:48.531
He will find a way to work this out.

08:48.591 --> 08:50.011
I'll go and ask Uncle now.

08:50.871 --> 08:52.171
I'll come with you.

08:54.401 --> 08:56.771
Have the kitchen prepare tea
that soothes the lungs

08:56.961 --> 08:59.221
and have someone clean
the room thoroughly.

08:59.231 --> 09:00.280
Make sure no dust or lint remains.

09:00.281 --> 09:01.421
Yes, Master.

09:01.991 --> 09:03.291
It's no big deal, my love.

09:03.831 --> 09:08.811
The pouch contains ephedra
that helps with breathing.

09:08.831 --> 09:10.131
It works.

09:11.831 --> 09:15.861
But the magnolias in the courtyard

09:16.111 --> 09:17.581
are in full bloom.

09:19.631 --> 09:20.771
That's right.

09:21.301 --> 09:22.891
You can't come into contact with pollen.

10:03.471 --> 10:04.630
Don't shake off the flowers.

10:04.631 --> 10:06.350
- Please stop shaking them off.
- This side.

10:06.351 --> 10:08.170
Why are you shaking off the flowers?

10:08.171 --> 10:09.230
- Keep shaking them off.
- Please stop!

10:09.231 --> 10:10.860
(Perpetual Bloom)
Stop it! Stop it!

10:10.861 --> 10:11.750
Ignore her. Keep shaking them off.

10:11.751 --> 10:13.981
Stop shaking them off! Stop it!

10:15.471 --> 10:16.611
Madam.

10:18.281 --> 10:21.291
Who told you to shake off the flowers?

10:21.561 --> 10:22.701
I did.

10:28.281 --> 10:29.421
Guqiu.

10:30.561 --> 10:32.461
This is just a temporary measure.

10:33.591 --> 10:35.581
Is taking a concubine also
a temporary measure?

10:35.751 --> 10:36.891
Or

10:37.631 --> 10:39.741
is the talk of heirs
and career advancement all lies?

10:41.351 --> 10:43.171
But the truth is you
have feelings for her.

10:43.961 --> 10:45.101
Am I right?

10:47.591 --> 10:48.731
Guqiu,

10:48.831 --> 10:50.101
Yingxue has asthma.

10:50.281 --> 10:51.581
These flowers cannot stay.

10:54.211 --> 10:55.891
Cannot stay, huh?

10:57.961 --> 10:59.131
All these years,

11:01.961 --> 11:03.080
I thought I was the only one

11:03.081 --> 11:05.221
who could make you smile

11:06.831 --> 11:09.741
and the only one
who could weigh on your heart.

11:11.081 --> 11:12.261
But I was so wrong.

11:16.401 --> 11:18.381
It turns out someone else can too.

11:19.871 --> 11:21.051
I'm begging you.

11:21.681 --> 11:23.341
Just this once.

11:41.511 --> 11:42.651
Go.

11:44.441 --> 11:45.771
Shake off the flowers.

11:48.041 --> 11:50.131
I knew you would understand me, Guqiu.

11:54.441 --> 11:55.981
Thank you, Guqiu.

11:58.871 --> 12:00.011
Hurry!

12:00.021 --> 12:01.040
- Shake off the flowers.
- Yes, Master.

12:01.041 --> 12:02.181
Get rid of all the flowers.

12:03.681 --> 12:04.821
Shake them off.

12:05.561 --> 12:06.701
This side too.

12:08.471 --> 12:09.611
Hurry.

12:10.681 --> 12:12.051
This side and that side too.

12:20.831 --> 12:23.570
Magnolias bloom without leaves.

12:23.571 --> 12:25.341
When there are leaves,
there are no flowers.

12:25.711 --> 12:28.101
They symbolize purity and loyalty,

12:28.491 --> 12:29.891
just like you and me.

12:30.681 --> 12:31.821
In this life,

12:32.581 --> 12:34.501
you're my only one.

12:37.321 --> 12:38.320
Be gentle.

12:38.321 --> 12:40.101
Don't damage the branches.

12:40.471 --> 12:42.501
They'll bloom again next year.

12:44.631 --> 12:48.291
(The hibiscus blooms in the morning
and withers by evening.)

12:48.751 --> 12:52.261
(I am no different from the flowers.)

13:05.231 --> 13:06.080
Eat some.

13:06.081 --> 13:07.981
Zhangru, I don't feel like eating.

13:09.631 --> 13:10.560
This won't do.

13:10.561 --> 13:11.560
Father told me

13:11.561 --> 13:12.891
to take good care of you two.

13:22.511 --> 13:24.051
Bad person! We don't need you to push.

13:30.561 --> 13:33.771
Do you also think that I'm a bad man?

13:35.111 --> 13:36.501
I don't know.

13:36.991 --> 13:39.870
But you built this swing for Mother.

13:39.871 --> 13:42.261
Will Miss Wang be the one
who rides it after this?

13:44.681 --> 13:45.821
No.

13:45.871 --> 13:47.011
This swing

13:47.471 --> 13:49.501
will always belong to you and Guqiu.

13:49.751 --> 13:51.101
No one else can have it.

13:51.801 --> 13:53.230
It's already a bit cramped

13:53.231 --> 13:54.741
when Zhangru and I sit on it together.

13:54.991 --> 13:57.861
If Mother and Miss Wang sat on it,

13:57.921 --> 13:59.651
how could they sit comfortably?

14:02.961 --> 14:04.341
I know

14:04.561 --> 14:06.621
that part of your heart is for Mother

14:07.201 --> 14:09.381
and part for Miss Wang.

14:09.871 --> 14:11.931
But have you ever asked yourself

14:12.111 --> 14:14.101
who's more important?

14:17.351 --> 14:20.131
Of course, it's you

14:20.871 --> 14:22.701
and your mother.

14:23.511 --> 14:25.440
Then why would you rather hurt Mother

14:25.441 --> 14:27.381
to keep Miss Wang here?

14:27.471 --> 14:30.771
Is… is taking her
as a concubine really the only way?

14:32.401 --> 14:33.541
Bad person!

14:34.511 --> 14:35.651
Ms. Longevity!

14:39.421 --> 14:40.510
(Tranquility and Serenity)

14:40.511 --> 14:41.651
Are you regretting it now?

14:41.831 --> 14:43.461
Are you trying to settle this
with money?

14:44.441 --> 14:46.131
If I must choose,

14:47.351 --> 14:49.131
I truly cannot bear

14:49.241 --> 14:51.181
to see both Guqiu
and Ms. Longevity heartbroken.

14:52.711 --> 14:53.851
It's already too late.

14:54.831 --> 14:56.080
Zou Er, tell him.

14:56.081 --> 14:57.221
Yes.

14:57.801 --> 14:58.740
Seventh Master,

14:58.741 --> 15:00.400
the physician who treated Ms. Wang

15:00.401 --> 15:01.541
says

15:01.781 --> 15:04.051
her fainting wasn't
because of asthma alone.

15:04.161 --> 15:06.891
She's been pregnant for over a month.

15:13.161 --> 15:14.931
I've let both Guqiu

15:15.831 --> 15:17.411
and Yingxue down.

15:17.471 --> 15:18.861
But if you don't take her in,

15:18.871 --> 15:21.101
you're dishonoring Father's memory.

15:21.631 --> 15:23.101
Do you remember

15:23.111 --> 15:24.931
the vow we made before his passing?

15:25.991 --> 15:27.531
To expand our lineage

15:28.681 --> 15:30.221
and restore the family's prestige.

15:30.441 --> 15:31.771
I'm glad you still remember.

15:32.511 --> 15:34.501
I've already lost two wives.

15:34.921 --> 15:38.101
Even if I wanted to remarry,
there's no suitable family left.

15:38.321 --> 15:40.011
All our hopes now rest on you.

15:40.441 --> 15:41.861
I will treat your children

15:41.871 --> 15:44.601
as my own and raise them with care.

15:44.681 --> 15:45.821
Shiying,

15:46.281 --> 15:47.501
take her as a concubine.

15:47.871 --> 15:49.861
It's the perfect solution

15:49.881 --> 15:51.461
for both your career and your lineage.

15:54.681 --> 15:56.051
Something bad has happened!

15:56.961 --> 15:58.101
Why is it so noisy?

16:00.831 --> 16:02.461
Fifth Master, Seventh Master.

16:02.751 --> 16:03.891
Seventh Madam is...

16:08.141 --> 16:09.641
(Serene)

16:16.711 --> 16:17.851
Madam...

16:18.631 --> 16:21.501
Mother, why?

16:23.471 --> 16:24.611
Madam...

16:35.961 --> 16:37.101
Issue my orders.

16:37.161 --> 16:38.301
Secure the gates

16:38.441 --> 16:39.990
and make sure no word of this gets out.

16:39.991 --> 16:41.131
At once, Seventh Master.

16:42.681 --> 16:44.381
Master...

16:49.991 --> 16:51.771
(The pristine magnolia,)

16:52.251 --> 16:54.011
(untouched by the impurities
of the world.)

16:54.991 --> 16:56.131
(My dear husband,)

16:56.991 --> 16:58.381
(every flower that blooms)

16:58.681 --> 17:00.101
(will eventually wither.)

17:00.801 --> 17:02.531
(Our marital fate has come to an end.)

17:03.471 --> 17:04.611
(I don't blame you.)

17:05.601 --> 17:07.030
(Perpetual Bloom)
(The only thing I feel guilty of)

17:07.031 --> 17:09.141
(and cannot let go of)

17:10.071 --> 17:11.501
(is Ms. Longevity.)

17:13.231 --> 17:15.611
(I need you to protect her
for the rest of her life.)

17:16.311 --> 17:17.981
(Make sure no one ever harms her.)

17:18.961 --> 17:20.611
(You must do this.)

17:23.361 --> 17:25.920
Mother stepped on this to hang herself.

17:25.921 --> 17:28.820
This is the surprise
she prepared for you.

17:28.821 --> 17:30.990
It's the Zhuangyuanhong wine
she buried on your wedding,

17:30.991 --> 17:33.771
wishing you success
in the imperial exams.

17:33.991 --> 17:35.400
She made your dreams

17:35.401 --> 17:37.701
her own!

17:38.511 --> 17:40.680
I should be punished.

17:40.681 --> 17:42.400
I spoke out of turn.

17:42.401 --> 17:44.531
When I found out
that Wang Yingxue was pregnant,

17:44.681 --> 17:47.901
I couldn't contain my anger
and told Madam.

17:47.921 --> 17:50.070
- I am to blame.
- Quiet!

17:50.071 --> 17:51.230
What nonsense!

17:51.231 --> 17:52.751
She was jealous and took her own life.

17:52.751 --> 17:53.941
She did it out of resentment.

17:54.121 --> 17:56.261
I won't let her ruin
the Dou Family's name.

17:56.791 --> 17:58.011
Listen carefully, all of you!

17:58.071 --> 17:59.661
Madam Zhao died of illness.

18:00.121 --> 18:02.611
Anyone who dares to speak recklessly
will be beaten to death.

18:03.751 --> 18:05.120
Adultery within the marriage

18:05.121 --> 18:06.531
and driving the wife to her death!

18:07.881 --> 18:09.611
Mr. Zhao, calm down...

18:09.991 --> 18:11.360
You got an heir you wanted

18:11.361 --> 18:13.070
- and ascended to noble connections!
- Mr. Zhao.

18:13.071 --> 18:15.331
Why don't you step over her corpse
and hold your wedding?

18:17.311 --> 18:20.470
I will risk my life and reputation

18:20.471 --> 18:23.701
to fight you to the bitter end!

18:25.121 --> 18:26.371
(The flowers have fallen.)

18:27.161 --> 18:28.301
(Mother,)

18:28.841 --> 18:32.011
(I thought you died
from a malicious plot.)

18:32.641 --> 18:36.141
(I didn't expect
that you would rather end your life)

18:36.921 --> 18:38.331
(than accept betrayal.)

18:39.621 --> 18:42.980
(Dou's Residence)

18:42.981 --> 18:47.081
(Funeral)

19:31.621 --> 19:33.470
- I'm sorry for your loss.
- I'm sorry for your loss.

19:33.471 --> 19:36.531
Thank you for your condolences,
Mr. Li. Mr. Liu.

19:37.791 --> 19:39.291
It's a tragic loss for the family.

19:39.711 --> 19:42.091
Madam Zhao
had always been weak in health.

19:42.441 --> 19:44.310
We thought it was just a slight cold.

19:44.311 --> 19:45.531
No one could have expected

19:45.641 --> 19:48.851
that she would pass away so suddenly.

19:48.921 --> 19:50.061
(Mother,)

19:50.511 --> 19:53.851
(your flowers won't fall anymore.)

20:09.531 --> 20:11.160
This is a place for kin.

20:11.161 --> 20:12.600
Are you from the Zhao or the Dou Family?

20:12.601 --> 20:13.771
Who are you to be here?

20:25.441 --> 20:26.661
Ms. Longevity, don't cry.

20:29.071 --> 20:30.611
Your mother has passed away.

20:30.751 --> 20:33.091
From now on, I will take her place
and care for you.

20:33.231 --> 20:35.461
I will treat you like my own daughter.

20:41.071 --> 20:42.211
Yingxue.

20:42.921 --> 20:44.061
Father.

20:46.121 --> 20:47.840
A life is lost

20:47.841 --> 20:50.510
and Dou Shiying spends
the whole day drinking in despair,

20:50.511 --> 20:51.741
only knowing to avoid.

20:51.811 --> 20:53.124
(Wang Xingyi, Vice Censor-in-Chief)
All the blame is

20:53.125 --> 20:55.091
(of the Right Censorate)
on you.

20:55.441 --> 20:58.181
Instead of being looked down upon
in the future,

20:58.881 --> 21:00.941
it would be better for you
to return with me now.

21:01.031 --> 21:04.261
I would rather my daughter
remain unmarried her entire life

21:05.031 --> 21:05.990
than become a concubine.

21:05.991 --> 21:07.750
Xingyi, it's a misunderstanding.

21:07.751 --> 21:10.261
We've announced to the public
that Madam Zhao died from illness.

21:10.331 --> 21:12.880
So your daughter will naturally take
her place as the main wife.

21:12.881 --> 21:14.270
The marriage will follow
the proper formalities and rites

21:14.271 --> 21:16.840
and the wedding banquet
will be held with full respect.

21:16.841 --> 21:19.501
The child she carries
is the legitimate heir of the family.

21:19.751 --> 21:22.371
The Dou Family will surely cherish it.

21:22.371 --> 21:24.510
This is the token to the treasury
of the Dou's Residence,

21:24.511 --> 21:26.781
which has always been kept
by the matron of the household.

21:26.791 --> 21:28.371
Now, I'll entrust it to your daughter.

21:28.511 --> 21:30.880
Whatever betrothal gifts,
or wedding items you need,

21:30.881 --> 21:33.120
Madam Zhao's bridal gifts
and personal belongings

21:33.121 --> 21:34.470
are at your disposal.

21:34.471 --> 21:37.041
(Dou's Residence)

21:37.991 --> 21:40.470
Send the list to my room later.

21:40.471 --> 21:42.710
From now on,
all the gifts from other families

21:42.711 --> 21:45.070
should be checked by me
before they are put into storage.

21:45.071 --> 21:46.211
- Yes.
- Yes.

22:04.991 --> 22:06.131
Mr. Zhao,

22:06.281 --> 22:08.331
why didn't you tell me you're coming?

22:08.511 --> 22:09.400
Perfect timing.

22:09.401 --> 22:10.810
I've made some fried dough.

22:10.811 --> 22:12.901
Let Dou Zhao and Zhangru have some.

22:13.311 --> 22:15.051
These are Guqiu's bridal gifts.

22:20.961 --> 22:23.011
That's the bracelet Aunt wore
when she was alive.

22:24.841 --> 22:25.981
Oh, really?

22:30.641 --> 22:32.501
- You!
- Listen here, Zhao.

22:32.711 --> 22:34.360
Now that Guqiu is dead,

22:34.361 --> 22:37.091
the marriage bond between the Zhao
and Dou Family has ended.

22:37.601 --> 22:40.981
I am now the legitimate wife.

22:41.471 --> 22:43.141
If you upset me,

22:43.401 --> 22:45.331
do you think
you can be here all the time?

22:46.271 --> 22:49.531
Aren't you afraid
I will vent all the frustration

22:49.621 --> 22:51.671
I've endured from you on Dou Zhao

22:52.031 --> 22:53.941
after you leave?

22:55.601 --> 22:56.771
It's tasty.

23:02.991 --> 23:05.221
Eat up if you think it's tasty.

23:05.751 --> 23:07.640
Just tell me what you like to eat.

23:07.641 --> 23:08.600
I'll make them for you.

23:08.601 --> 23:11.811
Ms. Longevity is really innocent
and naive.

23:12.231 --> 23:15.571
She forgets everything
when she sees a little snack.

23:20.361 --> 23:21.400
Miss Wang,

23:21.401 --> 23:23.141
my stomach really hurts.

23:24.791 --> 23:25.931
What's wrong?

23:30.271 --> 23:31.360
Ms. Longevity!

23:31.361 --> 23:32.210
You wicked woman!

23:32.211 --> 23:33.941
What did you give her?

23:33.991 --> 23:35.811
- Get the physician!
- Go quickly.

23:35.841 --> 23:37.981
- Go now.
- Ms. Longevity, spit it out!

23:39.921 --> 23:41.061
Come on.

23:48.681 --> 23:50.261
Poor child.

23:51.241 --> 23:53.241
(Old Madam Cui of the Dou Family)
I'm glad you're awake.

23:53.511 --> 23:54.651
Ms. Longevity,

23:54.961 --> 23:56.371
this is Madam Cui,

23:56.681 --> 23:58.221
your grandmother.

24:00.511 --> 24:02.011
Grandmother.

24:03.511 --> 24:04.651
Come.

24:06.601 --> 24:08.771
I don't blame you
for not recognizing me.

24:08.991 --> 24:12.221
I've long been estranged
from those two vile sons.

24:12.991 --> 24:15.990
If Guqiu hadn't written to me
before she hanged herself,

24:15.991 --> 24:17.421
asking me to watch over you,

24:17.591 --> 24:18.460
I can't imagine

24:18.461 --> 24:21.421
how many more people
they would have harmed.

24:22.551 --> 24:23.691
Ms. Longevity,

24:23.711 --> 24:26.011
what exactly had happened just now?

24:26.511 --> 24:29.291
Miss Wang smashed
my mother's bridal gift.

24:30.031 --> 24:32.981
She said I could get more snacks
if I was obedient.

24:33.161 --> 24:34.461
The physician said

24:34.681 --> 24:36.611
Ms. Longevity was poisoned by ephedra.

24:37.271 --> 24:38.981
Ephedra has a strong medicinal effect.

24:39.491 --> 24:41.640
For Wang Yingxue,
who suffers from asthma,

24:41.641 --> 24:43.510
it is a remedy she cannot be without.

24:43.511 --> 24:46.481
But it's poisonous to children.

24:46.791 --> 24:48.571
She wants to get rid of the child

24:48.811 --> 24:50.620
and seize the family's wealth.

24:50.621 --> 24:52.201
(Poisoned by ephedra)
You wicked woman!

24:52.201 --> 24:53.861
Both witnesses and evidence are present!

24:54.021 --> 24:55.441
You're still denying it!

24:55.541 --> 24:58.481
My daughter would never
do such lowly things.

24:58.481 --> 25:00.910
If there's any misunderstanding,
we can sit down and discuss it.

25:00.911 --> 25:03.921
According to the law,

25:04.281 --> 25:06.580
those who poison others
shall be executed.

25:06.581 --> 25:08.080
If the victim survived,

25:08.081 --> 25:10.740
they shall be punished with 100 strokes
and a prison sentence of three years.

25:10.741 --> 25:13.241
All three families are officials.

25:13.381 --> 25:15.521
If this matter is brought
to the emperor,

25:16.181 --> 25:18.681
can you tell His Majesty
that it's a misunderstanding?

25:19.501 --> 25:20.841
I did not poison her.

25:21.101 --> 25:23.401
I don't know
how she ended up eating ephedra.

25:23.741 --> 25:25.681
You've resided at the manor\
for a long time.

25:25.821 --> 25:28.140
How could you blame me

25:28.141 --> 25:29.380
based on a one-sided story?

25:29.381 --> 25:30.420
I cannot accept this.

25:30.421 --> 25:33.220
Since Old Madam is your mother-in-law,

25:33.221 --> 25:35.041
you should not defy
a senior family member.

25:35.421 --> 25:37.961
Old Madam is the only daughter
of the Ji'an Cui Clan.

25:37.961 --> 25:39.940
Her ancestors were meritorious officials
who helped found the kingdom

25:39.941 --> 25:41.220
and are revered in the imperial shrine.

25:41.221 --> 25:42.820
The Cui Clan has held
prestigious positions for generations,

25:42.821 --> 25:44.100
and half of the court officials

25:44.101 --> 25:46.761
are alumni of the Cui Clan Academy.

25:46.781 --> 25:48.321
This matter is reasonably justified.

25:48.661 --> 25:49.881
How can you not accept it?

25:50.101 --> 25:51.620
So Old Madam Dou is...

25:51.621 --> 25:53.020
My last name is Cui.

25:53.021 --> 25:54.561
I do not take my husband's last name.

25:54.661 --> 25:55.801
Please sit.

25:56.061 --> 25:57.801
If this goes to court,

25:57.931 --> 26:00.060
we all know what the outcomewill be.

26:00.061 --> 26:01.201
Mr. Wang,

26:01.251 --> 26:03.281
you risked being demoted

26:03.381 --> 26:06.220
to speak up against the horse market,

26:06.221 --> 26:08.241
which was known
among the scholars for your integrity.

26:08.261 --> 26:12.361
But just after your reinstatement,
you let your daughter act violently.

26:12.401 --> 26:14.401
What do you think
His Majesty would make of that?

26:14.541 --> 26:15.900
Your daughter forced a marriage

26:15.901 --> 26:17.780
that led to the main wife's suicide,

26:17.781 --> 26:21.041
poisoned the legitimate daughter,
and embezzled family assets.

26:21.441 --> 26:23.481
How should these three crimes

26:23.621 --> 26:25.041
be addressed, Mr. Wang?

26:27.981 --> 26:29.801
What do you suggest

26:30.661 --> 26:32.321
should be done about this?

26:34.981 --> 26:38.161
If the Dou and Wang families can
settle privately and offer compensation,

26:38.491 --> 26:41.761
it would give Ms. Longevity
a secure future.

26:41.981 --> 26:43.380
I've already ordered my son

26:43.381 --> 26:47.300
to transfer all of Guqiu's bridal gifts
to Dou Zhao's name

26:47.301 --> 26:49.401
with 3,000 taels in compensation.

26:49.621 --> 26:51.420
The Wang Family should match
that amount.

26:51.421 --> 26:52.561
That's impossible.

26:52.981 --> 26:55.041
The Dou Family was originally
a merchant family.

26:55.041 --> 26:56.881
Of course, they could afford
to offer that much.

26:57.461 --> 26:59.241
But my father just got reinstated.

26:59.461 --> 27:01.641
How could he fork out that much money?

27:01.701 --> 27:03.460
If you don't have it, you can borrow it.

27:03.461 --> 27:05.740
Over the years,
my sister had given you allowances

27:05.741 --> 27:07.841
worth at least over a hundred taels.

27:08.061 --> 27:10.921
Your father is a fourth-rank official.

27:10.941 --> 27:13.321
Borrowing a thousand taels
in cash shouldn't be difficult.

27:13.621 --> 27:14.761
As for the balance,

27:15.541 --> 27:18.201
you can write a promissory note
to pay it within five or ten years.

27:18.201 --> 27:19.700
You'll eventually clear
the balance anyhow.

27:19.701 --> 27:21.521
But Ms. Longevity is still young.

27:21.621 --> 27:23.460
How could she manage these finances?

27:23.461 --> 27:26.201
You don't need to worry about that.

27:27.021 --> 27:29.361
The one suffering is Ms. Longevity.

27:29.501 --> 27:31.521
What others say doesn't matter.

27:34.141 --> 27:35.761
Go and ask Ms. Longevity

27:35.981 --> 27:37.481
what she thinks.

27:37.901 --> 27:39.041
Yes, Madam Cui.

27:46.861 --> 27:49.241
The one truly suffering isn't me

27:49.701 --> 27:51.001
but my mother.

27:52.261 --> 27:54.521
She died
with a broken heart and regrets.

27:55.901 --> 27:58.121
If Miss Wang marries into the Dou Family

27:58.261 --> 28:00.001
and be my mother,

28:01.221 --> 28:03.201
how can my mother rest in peace?

28:03.421 --> 28:05.081
Ms. Longevity wants

28:05.181 --> 28:06.780
Miss Wang to kneel

28:06.781 --> 28:09.441
and mourn for her mother
for three years

28:09.441 --> 28:10.660
without marrying into the Dou Family.

28:10.661 --> 28:11.910
This is not right, Mother.

28:11.911 --> 28:13.340
If she doesn't marry into the family,

28:13.341 --> 28:15.900
how can her child
be properly recognized?

28:15.901 --> 28:17.540
We can't allow
the Dou Family's bloodline

28:17.541 --> 28:18.900
to wander outside aimlessly.

28:18.901 --> 28:20.281
If it's about status,

28:20.661 --> 28:22.680
a remarriage contract would suffice.

28:22.681 --> 28:24.721
I'm carrying the Dou Family's bloodline.

28:25.061 --> 28:26.721
What if the kneeling harms the child?

28:26.901 --> 28:28.721
After you marry into the household,

28:28.821 --> 28:31.401
you should meditate
at Youmin Temple for three years

28:31.541 --> 28:33.100
to repent and nurture your character.

28:33.101 --> 28:35.580
Don't let the karmic debt
affect the child.

28:35.581 --> 28:37.001
After the child is born,

28:37.621 --> 28:40.841
find a wet nurse
who knows how to educate children.

28:42.851 --> 28:43.980
Shiying,

28:43.981 --> 28:45.621
say something.

28:46.061 --> 28:47.841
I've failed Guqiu.

28:48.921 --> 28:50.681
I am willing to observe
the mourning period

28:51.001 --> 28:52.561
and live separately from the new wife.

28:53.621 --> 28:56.001
Yingxue will go to Youmin Temple.

28:56.381 --> 28:58.241
I will move into Guqiu's room.

28:58.861 --> 29:01.961
I will burn incense for her
and chant scriptures day and night.

29:07.361 --> 29:08.841
Forgive me.

29:08.981 --> 29:10.801
I am truly sorry for my mistakes.

29:10.971 --> 29:12.321
We will pay the compensation.

29:12.701 --> 29:16.441
Mother, please spare the child
in my womb.

29:19.741 --> 29:23.281
(Perpetual Bloom)

30:00.901 --> 30:02.521
Forgive me, Ms. Longevity.

30:03.181 --> 30:05.321
I can no longer stay
to watch you grow up.

30:06.701 --> 30:09.281
Mother, I don't blame you.

30:14.221 --> 30:16.121
I don't want to be your burden

30:17.261 --> 30:19.201
and see you suffering day and night.

30:20.621 --> 30:21.761
Don't worry about me.

30:23.161 --> 30:25.241
I will take good care of myself.

30:45.621 --> 30:47.041
(The magnolia has withered.)

30:47.901 --> 30:49.201
(The swing is covered in dust.)

30:50.701 --> 30:52.441
(This place is no longer your home,)

30:53.541 --> 30:54.841
(nor is it mine.)

30:56.701 --> 30:57.841
(Mother.)

30:58.621 --> 31:00.401
(If your spirit still lingers,)

31:01.521 --> 31:03.461
(I wish you could fly beyond
these high walls,)

31:04.061 --> 31:05.281
(over the courtyard,)

31:06.381 --> 31:07.721
(and find your freedom and peace.)

31:14.581 --> 31:17.940
(Cui's Residence)

31:17.941 --> 31:19.081
- Madam Cui.
- Madam Cui.

31:19.421 --> 31:20.561
Good.

31:20.941 --> 31:23.380
(Zhending, Cui Clan's Manor)

31:23.381 --> 31:24.841
This manor looks beautiful.

31:32.381 --> 31:33.580
- Greetings, Old Madam.
- Greetings, Old Madam.

31:33.581 --> 31:34.620
Ansu, hurry and greet the Old Madam.

31:34.621 --> 31:35.961
Greetings, Old Madam.

31:37.101 --> 31:39.121
These are Mr. and Mrs. Miao.

31:39.131 --> 31:41.220
They are our neighboring households
around the manor.

31:43.261 --> 31:44.460
When a new resident moves in,

31:44.461 --> 31:46.201
we sweep away the dust first.

31:46.421 --> 31:48.500
Get rid of the past
to make way for new beginnings.

31:48.501 --> 31:50.121
Then blessings and fortune will follow.

31:50.541 --> 31:51.881
This is yours.

31:52.541 --> 31:54.121
This is yours.

31:54.461 --> 31:56.201
You have one too.

31:58.021 --> 32:00.481
Grandmother, what flower is this?

32:00.821 --> 32:02.081
Purple crape myrtle.

32:02.621 --> 32:04.841
They are wildflowers
not worth mentioning.

32:04.941 --> 32:06.721
Peonies and orchids
are delicate beauties.

32:06.821 --> 32:08.921
But they compete fiercely for nutrients.

32:09.101 --> 32:10.460
They cannot endure heavy rain

32:10.461 --> 32:12.281
or drought

32:12.901 --> 32:14.801
and constantly require human care.

32:14.861 --> 32:16.761
Wildflowers are entirely different.

32:16.771 --> 32:18.771
They don't need favorable weather
or fertile land.

32:18.781 --> 32:22.601
Just scatter their seeds,
and they'll grow across the hills.

32:27.781 --> 32:31.201
You took the poison yourself
that day, didn't you?

32:32.101 --> 32:33.620
Ephedra is bitter.

32:33.621 --> 32:35.361
At a toxic dose,

32:35.781 --> 32:38.321
it would be so bitter
that one could hardly swallow it.

32:40.421 --> 32:41.841
This child is precocious

32:42.531 --> 32:44.241
and must hate me deeply.

32:44.861 --> 32:46.641
She'll be hard to manage in the future.

32:47.221 --> 32:48.481
She cannot be allowed to stay.

32:48.621 --> 32:50.801
Don't you have ephedra on you?

32:51.181 --> 32:53.140
That herb doesn't harm adults

32:53.141 --> 32:54.980
but not children.

32:54.981 --> 32:56.900
Even in small amounts,

32:56.901 --> 32:58.220
long-term use can drain

32:58.221 --> 33:01.641
one's energy, and weaken the lungs
and overall health.

33:02.581 --> 33:05.900
I will take great care of her

33:05.901 --> 33:07.401
and look after her in every way.

33:07.901 --> 33:11.881
I will look like a virtuous wife.

33:19.741 --> 33:21.761
Wang Yingxue leaves me with no choice.

33:22.021 --> 33:23.921
Instead of waiting for her to harm me,

33:24.781 --> 33:26.881
it's better to swallow
this bitterness myself

33:27.061 --> 33:28.481
to protect myself.

33:31.421 --> 33:32.561
Grandmother,

33:32.621 --> 33:34.441
I'm not a cruel person.

33:35.021 --> 33:36.361
I'm willing to risk my life

33:36.581 --> 33:38.281
to repay those who treat me well.

33:38.701 --> 33:39.980
If there's a grudge or hatred,

33:39.981 --> 33:41.841
even if it means hurting myself,

33:41.981 --> 33:43.641
I will return it.

33:48.491 --> 33:49.711
Ms. Longevity,

33:51.261 --> 33:52.561
you must remember this.

33:54.381 --> 33:57.361
You're not allowed to do this again.

33:57.621 --> 33:59.380
I took you away from that house

33:59.381 --> 34:01.841
because you're mature and intelligent.

34:02.381 --> 34:04.140
If you're trapped in family conflicts,

34:04.141 --> 34:06.060
you will become narrow-minded

34:06.061 --> 34:08.820
and focus on small and petty matters.

34:08.821 --> 34:11.141
Then you will miss out on
broader opportunities and growth.

34:11.901 --> 34:15.561
I want your intelligence
to go beyond that house,

34:15.821 --> 34:17.641
the mountains, rivers,

34:17.701 --> 34:19.401
and even the world.

34:19.581 --> 34:20.780
Those are the places

34:20.781 --> 34:22.761
where you can truly shine.

34:26.421 --> 34:28.300
My mother's bracelet.

34:28.301 --> 34:32.321
Broken things can shine again.

34:32.781 --> 34:33.921
Grandmother,

34:34.221 --> 34:35.401
I understand it now.

34:36.171 --> 34:37.540
I came to the countryside

34:37.541 --> 34:39.601
not to seek protection and dependence.

34:40.421 --> 34:44.300
But like the purple crape myrtle,
I'll be strong, resilient

34:44.301 --> 34:46.241
and able to withstand wind and rain.

34:46.821 --> 34:48.281
(From now on,)

34:48.461 --> 34:51.201
(I want to live a good life
for myself.)

34:56.701 --> 34:58.521
(I wish to study under a wise teacher)

34:58.741 --> 35:01.041
(Chen Qushui)
(to understand worldly matters.)

35:05.141 --> 35:06.281
Are you going to give or not?

35:06.781 --> 35:07.921
Are you deaf?

35:09.341 --> 35:10.180
Great comeback!

35:10.181 --> 35:13.900
Serve them right!

35:13.901 --> 35:14.990
Let me go!

35:14.991 --> 35:15.870
Let me go!

35:15.871 --> 35:17.581
Good job!

35:23.521 --> 35:26.140
(Then hire servants
who are trained in martial arts Sulan. Suxin)

35:26.141 --> 35:27.281
(for self-protection.)

35:32.901 --> 35:36.121
(Ultimately, I will make my way
into various businesses)

35:36.301 --> 35:37.601
(and prosper wherever I go.)

35:37.751 --> 35:38.640
Be careful.

35:38.641 --> 35:39.811
Give me a hand here.

35:56.021 --> 35:58.641
(Stable Foundation, Stable Nation)

36:02.861 --> 36:07.641
(Ding Army Barracks, Futing)

36:12.541 --> 36:13.681
Move it!

36:14.901 --> 36:16.041
Next!

36:17.621 --> 36:22.361
(Ding)

36:28.341 --> 36:30.900
Marshal, a kid came forward
to enlist in the army.

36:30.901 --> 36:31.780
Quick!

36:31.781 --> 36:33.140
We are guarding the border

36:33.141 --> 36:35.460
so that children can stay
with their families

36:35.461 --> 36:36.601
and free from harm.

36:36.741 --> 36:37.961
I do not take children in here.

36:38.181 --> 36:39.030
Send him away.

36:39.031 --> 36:40.064
(Yan Chaoqing)
Marshal,

36:40.065 --> 36:41.841
(Deputy General of the Ding Army)
you should take a look first.

36:43.021 --> 36:45.580
(Jiang Meisun, Duke of Ding)

36:45.581 --> 36:46.420
Keep up!

36:46.421 --> 36:47.420
(Young Song Mo)

36:47.421 --> 36:48.561
Hello, Marshal.

36:58.221 --> 36:59.620
Are you here to enlist in the army?

37:00.621 --> 37:02.201
You've lost your mind, kid!

37:02.531 --> 37:04.340
Did you run away from home
to join the army?

37:04.341 --> 37:05.300
Stop right there!

37:05.301 --> 37:06.500
Uncle, calm down.

37:06.501 --> 37:07.740
I didn't run away from home.

37:07.741 --> 37:09.060
I'm really here to join the army.

37:09.061 --> 37:10.920
Do you think joining the army is a game?

37:10.921 --> 37:12.620
Stop right there. Do you hear me?

37:12.621 --> 37:14.780
Kid, your father will ground you for a year

37:14.781 --> 37:17.180
if he finds out about this,
and I'm not going to plead for you.

37:17.181 --> 37:18.300
You only have two options now.

37:18.301 --> 37:20.380
Either you leave on your own,
or I'll take you back myself.

37:20.381 --> 37:21.220
Pick one.

37:21.221 --> 37:23.001
Then you'll have to tie me up first.

37:23.101 --> 37:24.580
Are you trying to mess with me?

37:24.581 --> 37:25.620
Someone, get him and tie him up!

37:25.621 --> 37:26.761
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

37:37.461 --> 37:38.540
Marshal,

37:38.541 --> 37:40.361
you need more men to catch him.

37:41.141 --> 37:43.281
I didn't expect him to be that fast.

37:44.901 --> 37:45.940
Why are you still here?

37:45.941 --> 37:47.060
Go and help out!

37:47.061 --> 37:48.201
Yes, sir.

37:53.381 --> 37:54.521
Your Lordship,

37:56.221 --> 37:57.180
with your build,

37:57.181 --> 37:59.321
you're still no match
for the pirates and their weapons.

37:59.321 --> 38:00.991
Do you think you can take on
the pirates?

38:02.741 --> 38:03.881
That's a bit...

38:04.941 --> 38:06.521
Am I able to fight the pirates now?

38:07.821 --> 38:09.020
Quite extraordinary.

38:09.021 --> 38:10.761
- Extraordinary indeed.
- Outrageous!

38:12.901 --> 38:14.041
Get down.

38:16.341 --> 38:17.481
Give me the dagger.

38:21.661 --> 38:23.161
You think you're that capable, huh?

38:23.501 --> 38:24.641
Send him home.

38:24.981 --> 38:26.121
Uncle.

38:26.421 --> 38:28.121
If you chase me away,

38:28.541 --> 38:30.481
I will truly be homeless.

38:38.461 --> 38:40.201
Did your father throw you out again?

38:42.781 --> 38:44.481
Ridiculous.

38:45.221 --> 38:47.281
What kind of father is Song Yichun?

38:47.981 --> 38:48.820
Uncle.

38:48.821 --> 38:49.820
I mean,

38:49.821 --> 38:50.780
Marshal,

38:50.781 --> 38:52.041
please take me in.

38:52.581 --> 38:55.681
I would go through fire and water
without hesitation for duty.

38:57.381 --> 38:59.001
Go through fire and water, huh?

38:59.201 --> 39:00.620
Can you even light a fire and cook?

39:00.621 --> 39:01.860
A cook?

39:01.861 --> 39:03.380
- How about something else?
- Do it, or leave.

39:03.381 --> 39:05.020
All right. I'll do it.

39:05.021 --> 39:06.161
Start working, then.

39:06.901 --> 39:08.041
Jiang Meisun,

39:08.061 --> 39:09.060
just you wait.

39:09.061 --> 39:11.601
One day, I will rise from a cook

39:11.781 --> 39:13.761
to a great general
who stabilizes the nation!

39:49.421 --> 39:50.761
Give it back to me.

39:55.501 --> 39:56.641
Hurry!

39:58.301 --> 39:59.441
Hurry.

40:02.221 --> 40:03.361
Look.

40:18.021 --> 40:20.700
Zhao sold off more than half
of the textile businesses in Guandong,

40:20.701 --> 40:22.761
as well as the rouge shops.

40:22.761 --> 40:25.460
She also bought dozens of silk factories
and tea plantations in Futing.

40:25.461 --> 40:27.380
(Miao Ansu)
The prices may be cheap.

40:27.381 --> 40:29.720
But these are all businesses
with slim profits and difficult sales.

40:29.741 --> 40:32.681
The Dongyu pirates
have been rampaging through Futing.

40:32.901 --> 40:35.001
Nine out of ten trading ships
are robbed by pirates.

40:35.101 --> 40:36.801
Wouldn't this be too risky?

40:39.341 --> 40:41.801
We have recaptured all the islands
along the coast.

40:42.501 --> 40:43.641
Let's cherish this moment.

40:43.741 --> 40:45.401
We don't have
many battles left to fight.

40:53.581 --> 40:55.721
(Records of the Enlightened Age)

40:57.401 --> 40:58.340
(Records of the Enlightened Age)

40:58.341 --> 41:00.700
The court has sent Duke of Ding

41:00.701 --> 41:02.340
to pacify the chaos at sea for years.

41:02.341 --> 41:05.051
The pirate troubles will be resolved,
and the sea trade will thrive.

41:05.061 --> 41:07.940
Things like silk and tea
may seem insignificant now.

41:07.941 --> 41:10.001
They will be more valuable
than gold in the future.

41:10.021 --> 41:12.460
So we need to quickly secure
these shops.

41:12.461 --> 41:13.980
They will double in value later.

41:13.981 --> 41:17.441
(Contract)

41:20.901 --> 41:22.561
(Records of the Enlightened Age)

41:23.861 --> 41:24.980
(Cloud Climber)

41:24.981 --> 41:26.820
(Sighing Gentleman)

41:26.821 --> 41:28.780
(Prodigious Monk)

41:28.781 --> 41:30.761
(Is everything in the dream)

41:31.061 --> 41:32.601
(Wrongfully Killed Man)
(going to happen?)

41:37.421 --> 41:38.561
Little child,

41:38.861 --> 41:40.201
why are you upset?

41:40.461 --> 41:41.980
(Records of the Enlightened Age)
I can't believe someone believed

41:41.981 --> 41:43.401
the random story I made up.

41:44.581 --> 41:47.161
What do you think
about the story I wrote?

41:47.861 --> 41:49.001
You wrote this?

41:50.621 --> 41:52.201
I clearly worked hard.

41:52.341 --> 41:54.201
Why can't I change the outcome?

41:54.421 --> 41:57.201
Throw a rock into the river.

41:59.021 --> 42:00.321
Throw a bigger one.

42:00.821 --> 42:02.801
A big one that it's difficult
for you to carry.

42:07.101 --> 42:08.220
(Did you see that?)

42:08.221 --> 42:10.100
No matter how large the rock is,

42:10.101 --> 42:12.361
it only creates a temporary ripple.

42:12.741 --> 42:15.681
You can't change
the direction of the river.

42:15.781 --> 42:19.940
Then how can one change
the direction of this river?

42:19.941 --> 42:21.281
If you have enough strength

42:21.341 --> 42:23.660
to make the majestic mountain

42:23.661 --> 42:26.001
in front of you collapse

42:26.061 --> 42:27.481
one day,

42:28.581 --> 42:32.681
then you can change the river.

42:46.661 --> 42:47.801
(So fate is not something)

42:48.061 --> 42:49.601
(that cannot be defied)

42:50.021 --> 42:51.161
(or changed.)

42:52.221 --> 42:53.361
(This time,)

42:53.901 --> 42:56.561
(I must obtain that strength)

42:59.221 --> 43:00.361
(to control)

43:00.901 --> 43:02.361
(my fate with my own hands.)

43:06.261 --> 43:07.740
(Ji Yong. Miao Ansu)

43:07.741 --> 43:09.180
(Dou Shishu, Cloud Climber)

43:09.181 --> 43:10.460
(Wang Yingxue)

43:10.461 --> 43:11.540
(Dou Shiying, Sorrowful Man.
An upright official, a loving father)

43:11.541 --> 43:12.820
(Jiang Meisun, Duke of Radiant Sea)

43:12.821 --> 43:14.140
(Crown Prince, Lord Qing)

43:14.141 --> 43:15.340
(The Emperor)

43:15.341 --> 43:18.401
(Dou Zhao)

43:23.261 --> 43:30.441
(Song Mo, Star of Doom)

43:42.981 --> 43:46.220
This family banquet is likely an opportunity
for the eldest grandson of Mr. Wu

43:46.221 --> 43:47.821
to meet the daughters of the Dou Family.

43:48.461 --> 43:50.700
Song Yichun neglected military affairs

43:50.701 --> 43:52.020
and shall be punished
with thirty lashes.

43:52.021 --> 43:52.860
I respectfully ask you

43:52.861 --> 43:54.901
to let me take the punishment
in place of my father.

43:54.941 --> 43:56.820
What a disappointment.

43:56.821 --> 43:58.131
Foolish!

43:58.421 --> 44:02.900
♪I lean in and gaze at you
as calm as serene waves♪

44:02.901 --> 44:06.661
♪I'm aware of the vast
and turbulent world♪

44:06.821 --> 44:11.211
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

44:11.391 --> 44:15.320
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

44:15.321 --> 44:18.300
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

44:18.301 --> 44:20.510
♪Or perhaps my heart yearns
for the other side♪

44:20.511 --> 44:23.071
♪Yet there's no place
for me to go in the end♪

44:23.121 --> 44:26.691
♪Your presence by my side
is irreplaceable♪

44:26.751 --> 44:30.271
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

44:30.281 --> 44:34.260
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

44:34.261 --> 44:38.291
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:38.731 --> 44:42.191
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:42.351 --> 44:44.531
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

44:44.551 --> 44:48.381
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

44:48.711 --> 44:51.851
♪Your presence by my side
is irreplaceable♪

44:52.391 --> 44:55.801
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

44:56.241 --> 44:59.781
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:59.981 --> 45:03.650
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

45:03.651 --> 45:07.991
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

45:08.051 --> 45:11.780
♪Having you is a blessing♪

45:11.781 --> 45:15.260
♪Only by being by your side♪

45:15.261 --> 45:19.941
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

45:19.971 --> 45:23.560
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

45:23.561 --> 45:27.701
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

45:27.771 --> 45:31.061
♪Always together, looking back♪

45:31.371 --> 45:38.671
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

45:47.901 --> 45:48.890
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:48.891 --> 45:49.850
(Every medical behavior involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:49.851 --> 45:51.121
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
